model.reports
Interface IPrintObject

All Known Implementing Classes:
PrintObject
public interface IPrintObject

This is the interface for a printable report object. The report object consists of 3 difference objects: - headers - text-blocks - tables The PrintObject will reference these object by the order in which they are built by the builder. The index starts at 0 This means that getHeader(1) will return the second header built by the builder.
